This token represents a liquidity pool on Curve, a leading decentralized exchange. Holders earn fees from users trading in the pool, and can also deposit the LP token on [ShapeShift](https://app.shapeshift.com/defi/earn) to earn yield. This liquidity pool contains [USDP](https://app.shapeshift.com/assets/eip155:1/erc20:0x1456688345527be1f37e9e627da0837d6f08c925) and [3CRV](https://app.shapeshift.com/assets/eip155:1/erc20:0x6c3f90f043a72fa612cbac8115ee7e52bde6e490). [3CRV](https://app.shapeshift.com/assets/eip155:1/erc20:0x6c3f90f043a72fa612cbac8115ee7e52bde6e490) is another curve LP token that consists of [DAI](https://app.shapeshift.com/assets/eip155:1/erc20:0x6b175474e89094c44da98b954eedeac495271d0f), [USDT](https://app.shapeshift.com/assets/eip155:1/erc20:0xdac17f958d2ee523a2206206994597c13d831ec7), and [USDC](https://app.shapeshift.com/assets/eip155:1/erc20:0xa0b86991c6218b36c1d19d4a2e9eb0ce3606eb48). To acquire crvUSDP, deposit [USDP](https://app.shapeshift.com/assets/eip155:1/erc20:0x1456688345527be1f37e9e627da0837d6f08c925), [DAI](https://app.shapeshift.com/assets/eip155:1/erc20:0x6b175474e89094c44da98b954eedeac495271d0f), [USDT](https://app.shapeshift.com/assets/eip155:1/erc20:0xdac17f958d2ee523a2206206994597c13d831ec7), and/or [USDC](https://app.shapeshift.com/assets/eip155:1/erc20:0xa0b86991c6218b36c1d19d4a2e9eb0ce3606eb48) on [Curve](https://curve.fi/usdp/deposit). Please be aware that as liquidity pools are composed of differently-priced assets, they are subject to impermanent loss but because all of the assets in the pool are pegged to $1, impermanent loss is unlikely and would only result if one of the assets in the pool lost its peg. 